title: Relatable.
text: Overall I love instagram , I love the reels and love to watch them when I am feeling down and it makes me smile when I cry and I can communicate to my friends if I get my phone took I can just log into my account on my friends phone if I get mines took , I love instagram it makes me feel better about myself and lets me edit my pictures and choose the coloring I was on my video/pictures . Instagram is a wonderful app if you actually can relate to a lot of content as well like quotes .. most of the quotes that pop up on my fyp are so relatable and it makes me feel good that I am not the only one struggling and know that there is other people out there that understand how I feel , so at the end of the day instagram is the most wonderful app that I have been on in my in tire life , I love you guys❤️.
